WEBVTT

00:02:59.170 --> 00:03:01.167
It would then sit and wait.

00:03:01.755 --> 00:03:04.766
It would wait until you logged
into your bank account.

00:03:05.299 --> 00:03:08.642
And when you did,
the bad guys would reach in,

00:03:08.666 --> 00:03:10.319
steal your credentials,

00:03:10.343 --> 00:03:12.244
and then use that to steal your money.

00:03:13.023 --> 00:03:14.943
This sounds terrible,

00:03:14.967 --> 00:03:17.760
but the reality is,
in the security industry,

00:03:17.784 --> 00:03:21.466
this form of attack
is somewhat commonplace.

